about.summary: Functions and datasets for bootstrapping from the book "Bootstrap Methods and Their Application" by A. C. Davison and  D. V. Hinkley (1997, CUP), originally written by Angelo Canty for S.

name: r-boot
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.3-24" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-boot
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/boot_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/boot/boot_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 89d4596d4a1287155597257372a872b04fbd406cd23fd8436f8e56394ba1607b

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('boot')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('boot')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=boot
  license: Unlimited
  summary: Functions and datasets for bootstrapping from the book "Bootstrap Methods and Their
    Application" by A. C. Davison and  D. V. Hinkley (1997, CUP), originally written
    by Angelo Canty for S.
  license_family: MIT

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
    - conda-forge/r
